### Referral - REST Client requests (authenticated)

### Get referral code
GET {{base}}/api/v1/referral/code
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Generate new referral code
POST {{base}}/api/v1/referral/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Get referral earnings
GET {{base}}/api/v1/referral/earnings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get referral stats
GET {{base}}/api/v1/referral/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get referral history (paginated)
GET {{base}}/api/v1/referral/history?limit={{limit}}&offset={{offset}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Curl examples

# Get referral code
# curl -H "Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>" {{base}}/api/v1/referral/code

# Generate new code
# curl -X POST -H "Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>" -H "Content-Type: application/json" {{base}}/api/v1/referral/generate -d '{}'

# Get earnings
# curl -H "Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>" {{base}}/api/v1/referral/earnings

# Get stats
# curl -H "Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>" {{base}}/api/v1/referral/stats

# Get history
